ork or Washington, so please give a shout if you=E2=80=99d like to get toge=
ther.<br/><br/>In tonight=E2=80=99s edition of In the Room, news and notes =
on some of the industry=E2=80=99s myriad fixations <i>du jour</i>: the Cond=
=C3=A9 Nast layoffs, <b>Stephen A. Smith</b>=E2=80=99s new deal, the latest=
 <b>Taylor Lorenz </b>scandal, etcetera.<br/><br/>=F0=9F=8E=99=EF=B8=8F=F0=
=9F=8D=B8 On <u><a href=3D"https://email.puck.news/e/c/eyJlbWFpbF9pZCI6ImRn=
